{"tid":2069292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南早：海航旗下香港航空　要求港府一視同仁泵水救亡","createTime":"2020-06-18T09:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T00:08:54.000Z","uid":241764,"like":4,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7fd7e26b2d7a9f9d69c27a65aa78df2dc8e626","tid":2069292,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9-%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%96%E5%90%8C%E4%BB%81%E6%B3%B5%E6%B0%B4%E6%95%91%E4%BA%A1/?fbclid=IwAR3JOIccXZfooAwa2n45KBa72OfHQ142FCl9eiXWuw-hlzr2qAGWMRF7kpY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%2588%25AA%25E6%2597%2597%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BB%2581%25E6%25B3%25B5%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25BA%25A1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3JOIccXZfooAwa2n45KBa72OfHQ142FCl9eiXWuw-hlzr2qAGWMRF7kpY&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=9f70a850\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%2588%25AA%25E6%2597%2597%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BB%2581%25E6%25B3%25B5%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25BA%25A1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3JOIccXZfooAwa2n45KBa72OfHQ142FCl9eiXWuw-hlzr2qAGWMRF7kpY&h=e48329f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9-%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%96%E5%90%8C%E4%BB%81%E6%B3%B5%E6%B0%B4%E6%95%91%E4%BA%A1/?fbclid=IwAR3JOIccXZfooAwa2n45KBa72OfHQ142FCl9eiXWuw-hlzr2qAGWMRF7kpY</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情重創航空業務。港府日前宣布出手拯救國泰，以認購優先股及貸款等方式共注資近 300 億元。據《南華早報》今日報道，海航旗下的香港航空亦正要求港府泵水救亡。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》引述香港航空稱，希望政府可以考慮其近期的航空業救助計劃，能夠一併支援其他以香港作為基地航空公司，指他們同樣有份致力維持香港航空樞紐的地位。<br />\n<br />\n香港航空又指，公司自 2006 年以來，一直為香港國際機場的客運及貨運量作出貢獻，而疫情導致航空業癱瘓，大部分航班都要停運，「我們致力為香港服務，並一直對強大的戰略投資者持開放態度，以確保我們的長期發展」。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指，自今年 1 月以來，香港航空已從中資銀行獲得超過 10 億元人民幣的額外資金，用作償還到期債務。這筆財政支援令香港政府「暫時」未需要出手拯救港航。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正向香港航空查詢。<br />\n<br />\n早前香港政府決定出手拯救國泰航空，一家由政府擁有的全資公司將會認購國泰優先股，總金額 195 億元，以及行使價為 19.5 億元的認股權證；政府的全資公司又會向國泰提供 78 億元已承擔過渡貸款融資。政府將有權委任兩名觀察員出席國泰董事會會議。"},{"pid":"c6cbae2e83c5abd1ef86058d32db5fc0440d5bed","tid":2069292,"uid":5789,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"有冇武肺佢都遲早收皮, 泵水比佢等如直接比上面"},{"pid":"03576f8ce7a20a757194846f64ebf3898977de89","tid":2069292,"uid":46906,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"迪士尼：#metoo"},{"pid":"1def3f287aa6aa50f200ee300edc39a279f11e3a","tid":2069292,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"香港航空重未refund<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 已經講左幾個月"},{"pid":"5d202d0a56fd0244e908153c3308009ef8ffee1a","tid":2069292,"uid":359260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:28:08.000Z","msg":"佢有國家救 洗咩香港政府幫<br />\n<br />\n<del>亞視</del>永恆萬歲"},{"pid":"be88a4fa82630ac06dcb7cef79d9a4b58f47b202","tid":2069292,"uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6cbae2e83c5abd1ef86058d32db5fc0440d5bed","tid":2069292,"uid":5789,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"有冇武肺佢都遲早收皮, 泵水比佢等如直接比上面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"根本係政府用香港人(外匯)找數比支那"},{"pid":"fb02d3526069b3974290c9637dac4ed1e81e816d","tid":2069292,"uid":152225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s